CREATE TABLE EotStreamsForwardedStreams (TransmitPort TEXT, TxFrames INTEGER, RxFrames INTEGER, FrameLoss INTEGER, TargetReceivePort TEXT)

INSERT INTO EotStreamsForwardedStreams SELECT tx.PortName, tx.FrameCount, (rx.FrameCount - rx.DuplicateFrameCount), (tx.FrameCount - (rx.FrameCount - rx.DuplicateFrameCount)), tx.RxPortName FROM TxEotStreamResults AS tx INNER JOIN RxEotStreamResults AS rx WHERE tx.StreamId=rx.Comp32 AND rx.IsExpectedPort=1 AND tx.ParentHnd IN (SELECT Handle FROM MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_WestPortGroupHandles)
CREATE TABLE EotStreamsNonForwardedStreams (TransmitPort TEXT, TxFrames INTEGER, RxFrames INTEGER, FrameLoss INTEGER, TargetReceivePort TEXT)

INSERT INTO EotStreamsNonForwardedStreams SELECT tx.PortName, tx.FrameCount, 0, tx.FrameCount, tx.RxPortName FROM TxEotStreamResults AS tx  WHERE tx.StreamId NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT Comp32 FROM RxEotStreamResults) AND tx.ParentHnd IN (SELECT Handle FROM MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_WestPortGroupHandles)

INSERT INTO EotStreamsNonForwardedStreams SELECT tx.PortName, tx.FrameCount, 0, tx.FrameCount, tx.RxPortName FROM TxEotStreamResults AS tx  WHERE tx.StreamId IN (SELECT DISTINCT Comp32 FROM RxEotStreamResults WHERE Comp32 NOT IN ( SELECT DISTINCT Comp32 FROM RxEotStreamResults WHERE IsExpectedPort=1)) AND tx.ParentHnd IN (SELECT Handle FROM MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_WestPortGroupHandles)
SELECT * FROM EotStreamsNonForwardedStreams

CREATE TABLE EotTPortFloodedStreamResults AS SELECT tx.ParentHnd AS 'Handle', (SELECT Location FROM Port WHERE Handle=tx.ParentHnd) AS 'TxPortLocation', rx.FrameCount AS 'StrayRxFrames', (SELECT Location FROM Port WHERE Handle=rx.ParentHnd) AS 'RxPortLocation' FROM TxEotStreamResults AS tx INNER JOIN RxEotStreamResults AS rx WHERE tx.StreamId=rx.Comp32 AND rx.IsExpectedPort=0 AND tx.ParentHnd IN (SELECT Handle FROM MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_WestPortGroupHandles) AND rx.ParentHnd IN (SELECT Handle FROM MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_WestPortGroupHandles) AND rx.FrameCount!=0

CREATE TABLE EotLPortFloodedStreamResults AS SELECT tx.ParentHnd AS'Handle', (SELECT Location FROM Port WHERE Handle=tx.ParentHnd) AS 'TxPortLocation', rx.FrameCount AS 'StrayRxFrames', (SELECT Location FROM Port WHERE Handle=rx.ParentHnd) AS 'RxPortLocation' FROM TxEotStreamResults AS tx INNER JOIN RxEotStreamResults AS rx WHERE tx.StreamId=rx.Comp32 AND rx.IsExpectedPort=0 AND tx.ParentHnd IN (SELECT Handle FROM MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_WestPortGroupHandles) AND rx.ParentHnd IN (SELECT Handle FROM MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_EastPortGroupHandles) AND rx.FrameCount!=0

CREATE TABLE EotMPortFloodedStreamResults AS SELECT tx.ParentHnd AS'Handle', (SELECT Location FROM Port WHERE Handle=tx.ParentHnd) AS 'TxPortLocation', rx.FrameCount AS 'StrayRxFrames', (SELECT Location FROM Port WHERE Handle=rx.ParentHnd) AS 'RxPortLocation' FROM TxEotStreamResults AS tx INNER JOIN RxEotStreamResults AS rx WHERE tx.StreamId=rx.Comp32 AND rx.IsExpectedPort=0 AND tx.ParentHnd IN (SELECT Handle FROM MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_WestPortGroupHandles) AND rx.ParentHnd IN (SELECT Handle FROM MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_SouthPortGroupHandles) AND rx.FrameCount!=0
UPDATE MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_CurrentIteration SET NumberOfAddresses=(SELECT NumberOfAddresses FROM MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_CurrentIteration)
UPDATE MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_CurrentIteration SET Load=((SELECT Load FROM MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_CurrentIteration) * (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_EastPortGroupHandles))

UPDATE MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_CurrentIteration SET TPortTxFrames=(SELECT Sum(GeneratorSigFrameCount) FROM GeneratorPortResults WHERE ParentPort IN (SELECT Handle FROM MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_WestPortGroupHandles))

UPDATE MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_CurrentIteration SET TPortFloodCount=(SELECT CASE WHEN (SELECT Count(*) FROM EotTPortFloodedStreamResults)=0 THEN 0 ELSE (SELECT Sum(StrayRxFrames) FROM EotTPortFloodedStreamResults) END)
UPDATE MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_CurrentIteration SET LPortRxFrames=(SELECT Sum(RxFrames) FROM EotStreamsForwardedStreams)

UPDATE MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_CurrentIteration SET LPortFloodCount=(SELECT CASE WHEN (SELECT Count(*) FROM EotLPortFloodedStreamResults)=0 THEN 0 ELSE (SELECT Sum(StrayRxFrames) FROM EotLPortFloodedStreamResults) END)

UPDATE MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_CurrentIteration SET MPortFloodCount=(SELECT CASE WHEN (SELECT Count(*) FROM EotMPortFloodedStreamResults)=0 THEN 0 ELSE (SELECT Sum(StrayRxFrames) FROM EotMPortFloodedStreamResults) END)
UPDATE MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_CurrentIteration SET TotalFloodCount=(SELECT TPortFloodCount + LPortFloodCount + MPortFloodCount FROM MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_CurrentIteration)
UPDATE MethRfc2889AddrLearnRate_CurrentIteration SET Verdict='FAIL'
CREATE TABLE EotFloodedStreamResults (Handle INTEGER, TxPortLocation TEXT, StrayRxFrames INTEGER, RxPortLocation TEXT)
INSERT INTO EotFloodedStreamResults (Handle , TxPortLocation , StrayRxFrames , RxPortLocation) SELECT * FROM  EotTPortFloodedStreamResults
INSERT INTO EotFloodedStreamResults (Handle , TxPortLocation , StrayRxFrames , RxPortLocation) SELECT * FROM  EotLPortFloodedStreamResults
INSERT INTO EotFloodedStreamResults (Handle , TxPortLocation , StrayRxFrames , RxPortLocation) SELECT * FROM  EotMPortFloodedStreamResults

CREATE TABLE TestConfiguration (NumberOfPort INTEGER,NumberOfAddresses INTEGER, FrameSizes TEXT, NumberOfTrials INTEGER, SearchRateResolution INTEGER, InitialSearchRate INTEGER, MinimumSearchRate INTEGER, MaximumSearchRate INTEGER, AddressRateTestCriteria INTEGER, SutAgingTime INTEGER, StartTrafficDelay INTEGER, WaitAfterTraffic INTEGER)

INSERT INTO TestConfiguration VALUES (NULL,NULL,(SELECT ValueList FROM spirent_methodology_ObjectIteratorCommand WHERE ParentHnd IN (SELECT SourceHnd FROM RelationTable WHERE TargetHnd=(SELECT Handle FROM Tag WHERE Name='WhileFrameSize') AND Type='UserTag')),NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL)
UPDATE TestConfiguration SET FrameSizes=REPLACE(FrameSizes,' ',',')

UPDATE TestConfiguration SET NumberOfTrials=(SELECT MaxVal FROM spirent_methodology_ObjectIteratorCommand WHERE ParentHnd IN (SELECT SourceHnd FROM RelationTable WHERE TargetHnd=(SELECT Handle FROM Tag WHERE Name='WhileTrials') AND Type='UserTag'))

UPDATE TestConfiguration SET MinimumSearchRate=(SELECT MinVal FROM spirent_methodology_ObjectIteratorCommand WHERE ParentHnd IN (SELECT SourceHnd FROM RelationTable WHERE TargetHnd=(SELECT Handle FROM Tag WHERE Name='WhileLoads') AND Type='UserTag'))

UPDATE TestConfiguration SET MaximumSearchRate=(SELECT MaxVal FROM spirent_methodology_ObjectIteratorCommand WHERE ParentHnd IN (SELECT SourceHnd FROM RelationTable WHERE TargetHnd=(SELECT Handle FROM Tag WHERE Name='WhileLoads') AND Type='UserTag'))

UPDATE TestConfiguration SET SutAgingTime=(SELECT WaitTime FROM WaitCommand WHERE Handle IN (SELECT SourceHnd FROM RelationTable WHERE TargetHnd IN (SELECT Handle FROM Tag WHERE Name='WaitSutAgingTime') AND Type='UserTag'))

UPDATE TestConfiguration SET StartTrafficDelay=(SELECT WaitTime FROM WaitCommand WHERE Handle IN (SELECT SourceHnd FROM RelationTable WHERE TargetHnd IN (SELECT Handle FROM Tag WHERE Name='WaitStartTrafficDelay') AND Type='UserTag'))

UPDATE TestConfiguration SET WaitAfterTraffic=(SELECT WaitTime FROM WaitCommand WHERE Handle IN (SELECT SourceHnd FROM RelationTable WHERE TargetHnd IN (SELECT Handle FROM Tag WHERE Name='WaitWaitAfterTrafficStopped') AND Type='UserTag'))
